{"tid":263243,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[純討論]如果你知道你朋友殺咗人，會點做？","createTime":"2017-05-29T22:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T13:51:53.000Z","uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ef276391ceeef312bcd4a920080072350a172a","tid":263243,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T22:27:05.000Z","msg":"朋友大分三種<br />\n1.老死(生死之交，投名狀)<br />\n2.朋友(平時都幾要好，成日見面一齊玩一齊飲飲食食)<br />\n3.普通朋友(即係好勉強算係朋友，喺你心目中極其量叫做識，喺街撞到會say hi嗰啲，可能同同事都frd過同呢啲人)<br />\n<br />\n殺人分幾個類型<br />\nA.錯手殺人(可能推撞之下唔小心撞咗佢個頭落鐵釘之類)<br />\nB.老謀(好似今次引死者上山嗰孖田咁，已經有部署過)<br />\nC.冷血殺人(例如連環殺人，弒親，殘忍殺人，殺完人同屍體/屍塊自拍做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> V手勢)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果以我嚟計，我嘅做法：<br />\n1A我會提供協助，例如幫忙著草，金錢援助<br />\n如果佢求我幫佢一齊處理屍體嘅話我唔會一口答應<br />\n但佢苦苦哀求我估我都會幫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢都係錯手殺咗人啫，又唔係有心，最多比人拉到咪告你非法處理屍體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少我真係盡咗力而又喺我嘅道德立場之內對呢份友誼完全付出<br />\n如果要我幫手分屍，燒屍我都唔會做得出，最多幫手推佢落山呀，落海呀，掘個窿埋咗佢<br />\n<br />\n1B我唔會提供協助，但我都唔會報警，我會勸佢自首，如果勸唔到就唯有扮唔知算，喺香港老謀99%走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n1C我會指責佢，不停咁哦鳩佢叫佢快撚啲去自首，軟硬兼施，又求又哦，如果到最後都唔肯去，唯有等警察自己搵到佢，一樣都唔會報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2A嘅話我唔會提供任何協助，至多至多扮乜都唔知算<br />\n2B2C會直接報警<br />\n<br />\n3A3B3C乜都唔會講，報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed5f917308d78400bb382e6bf680040163250b9","tid":263243,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T22:57:16.000Z","msg":"全部都會報警"},{"pid":"c49e655cd1c4583ababc926512a88c5e3f85491b","tid":263243,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:09:20.000Z","msg":"等安全情況先報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好打草驚蛇 陣間殺埋你"},{"pid":"c3e506be05213cc3c577296a7e0b0353b6242e2f","tid":263243,"uid":107844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同你講依件事真係發生左係我身上<br />\n1A，1B都有<br />\n嗰下真係改變我成個世界觀(不在現場，件事過左好耐，佢後來同我懺悔)<br />\n不過而家仲係好朋友<br />\n但已經覺得人要殺另外一個人其實好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至畀人當失蹤連公道都攞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我相信依件事真係發生左既話，樓主肯定冇咁冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d311b258dd127cf480b74f52c21e18ea7f764649","tid":263243,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:44:41.000Z","msg":"金手指篤背脊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6783f57cc6968591273138cef5b7011bf1734ad4","tid":263243,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T02:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同你講依件事真係發生左係我身上<br />\n1A，1B都有<br />\n嗰下真係改變我成個世界觀(不在現場，件事過左好耐，佢後來同我懺悔)<br />\n不過而家仲係好朋友<br />\n但已經覺得人要殺另外一個人其實好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至畀人當失蹤連公道都攞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我相信依件事真係發生左既話，樓主肯定冇咁冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n警察有冇拉你朋友？唔好包庇"},{"pid":"3c0ad3e1a88f2231e4b07c9775512903be78038c","tid":263243,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全部都會報警</blockquote><br />\n其實真係睇交情同嚴重程度<br />\n十幾年交情 如果錯手殺人 又唔係有心<br />\n我都唔忍心要睇住佢比人困住"},{"pid":"3becc68f6b05053c6ccf6368a162e373e5a60584","tid":263243,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等安全情況先報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好打草驚蛇 陣間殺埋你</blockquote><br />\n2B,2C 同 3 會用呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc4e32cf6e887c1d5855ec94e2069127ea5f136","tid":263243,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同你講依件事真係發生左係我身上<br />\n1A，1B都有<br />\n嗰下真係改變我成個世界觀(不在現場，件事過左好耐，佢後來同我懺悔)<br />\n不過而家仲係好朋友<br />\n但已經覺得人要殺另外一個人其實好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至畀人當失蹤連公道都攞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我相信依件事真係發生左既話，樓主肯定冇咁冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺人真係好易<br />\n我有同事幾歲嗰陣唔小心殺咗個同佢一樣大嘅小妹妹<br />\n不過當時喺大陸 屋企人又有權有勢先壓咗落嚟<br />\n你問我會唔會咁冷靜<br />\n就梗係會六神無主啦<br />\n但好朋友始終係好朋友<br />\n人地喺你有事嗰陣義無反顧咁幫你<br />\n呢啲人情點都要盡還"},{"pid":"4316aa09c7f1f73929988b533f0a6e2c25eaef6e","tid":263243,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金手指篤背脊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有部分人都會同你一樣咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同事話佢連親生細佬都會篤"},{"pid":"c50e023885ee31bdabc641d2c657d442be0d6225","tid":263243,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金手指篤背脊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有部分人都會同你一樣咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同事話佢連親生細佬都會篤</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6ab97799732bc46ae8922eb26150735229b844","tid":263243,"uid":107844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同你講依件事真係發生左係我身上<br />\n1A，1B都有<br />\n嗰下真係改變我成個世界觀(不在現場，件事過左好耐，佢後來同我懺悔)<br />\n不過而家仲係好朋友<br />\n但已經覺得人要殺另外一個人其實好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至畀人當失蹤連公道都攞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我相信依件事真係發生左既話，樓主肯定冇咁冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n警察有冇拉你朋友？唔好包庇</blockquote><br />\n都話當左失蹤人口，如果唔係佢點同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個世界唔係非黑即白，法律都只不過係人訂<br />\n不過我信有因果，都見佢啲報開始黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708e1380e5e663e5caf669f3449dcd1392748027","tid":263243,"uid":48428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"1c樓主咁我驚變下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1a,1b,2a,2b我都會扮唔知算<br />\nc就全部報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8214d5218aa435c28ea7d736c37932c165fb90b2","tid":263243,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"唔會理"},{"pid":"768a4ebf63bdfcc1297f037624b3be5d7fd010f2","tid":263243,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T13:51:53.000Z","msg":"全部都質佢食龍蝦屎"}]}